title: Alex Jones Show - 2012 Mar 02 FR [sebaygo1]

The Alex Jones Show
Friday, 02 March 2012


[sebaygo1]


Show Description
................

From the Infowars web site ::

Alex continues coverage of the untimely and suspicious death of journalist and alternative media pioneer Andrew Breitbart who was to release damning info on Obama on March 1. 

Alex also talks with Delegate Glen Glass and Legislative aide Aaron Jones of the Maryland House of Delegates. Glass has introduced legislation to stop TSA groping and would force the privatization of security at airports in the state. Glass has also introduced a bill that would allow Marylanders to opt out of the smart meter program.

Though not billed in the official show description, in the 3rd hour Alex talks with Bob Chapman and then Dr. Jerome Cosrsi.
